text: The following countries had a census of the general population in 2000: * Fifth National Population Census of the People's Republic of China * Costa Rica 2000 Census, the ninth federal census, conducted at irregular intervals * 2000 Estonia Census * Indonesia 2000 census * 2000 Panamanian census * 2000 Turkish census * 2000 United States Census, the 22nd decennial federal census
title: 2000 Census
